**Description of the Application**
GABES is a software application developed as part of the PhD thesis work of the
author at the National Polytechnic School of Algiers (ENP). The development of this
work has been conducted under the PhD framework and for academic research purposes.
GABES implements the Boundary Element Method (BEM) for homogeneous elastostatic problems
and includes a graphical interface for visualization and post-processing.

